      "rationale": "Both Ansys and the FDA in-house FEA solver are operated under documented quality management systems with regression test suites. Version control and change management records confirm no unvalidated code changes were introduced during the study period. Required level 2 (documented QMS) achieved and exceeded at level 3 (independent regression verification)."
