      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably equivalent to experimental specimen and test configuration; any deviations quantified and their effect on QoIs bounded.",
      "rationale": "FEA geometry derived from CMM measurements of the actual test specimens. Boundary conditions replicate fixture geometry to within 0.1 mm. Material inputs from same lot as test specimens. Sensitivity analysis confirms that residual geometric deviations (<0.01 mm) contribute <0.3% to QoI uncertainty. Required level 3 met."
    },
