    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against required level 3 due to single load condition; this shortfall is accepted because ASTM F1717 specifies a single canonical test condition and the regulatory submission is limited to that condition. The E/uval metric (methodology referenced via doi:10.1016/j.ymeth.2024.03.003) confirms adequate agreement for all three QoIs. Overall credibility is sufficient for the Medium model risk / Medium decision consequence context. Package accepted.",
